					<h1>The Spot Gold Price Today With 200 Day Moving Average Gold Chart</h1>
					<p class="headline_meta"><span><a href="http://www.runtogold.com/metal-prices/gold-price-and-gold-prices/#comments" rel="nofollow">14 comments</a></span></p>
